      "recording_attendee_id": "f0fd6c0d-3f93-4463-81a3-a7ef168b4130",
      "order_number": 3,
      "text": "Um You might be reading my emails. This is Andy key from rentable. Um I reached out to her, we we're an internet listing site. I was just hoping to connect with whoever handles your I guess marketing or online, leasing posting stuff of that nature. Would that be you?"
